  <brief_title>The Effect of Nitric Oxide on Spatial Working Memory in Patients With Schizophrenia - Pilot Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Nitric Oxide on Spatial Working Memory in Patients With Schizophrenia - Pilot Study</official_title>
